review_content: Used it in my first Gaming PC build with a RTX 3060 ti today. Amazing performance !! It's the best budget CPU at this price range and also one of the best budget CPU Intel has ever built. It rarely bottlenecks the RTX 3060 ti in gaming. Only bottlenecks in extremely CPU heavy games like RDR2 when played on 1080p resolution. So I would suggest you to play on 1440p resolution if your monitor supports it as it becomes less CPU bound and more GPU bound which will almost eliminate any kind of bott...

Very poor packaging, but good experience overall. Product was delivered in factory sealed box (which was scuffed and banged about in transport quite a lot, so it looks really old but it's not) and works well. I already have the one with iGPU doing HTPC duty, and this is one is used to replace an old 3rd Gen Xeon, so it's a big step up. Pricing was better than offline retail, but the poor handling is quite a let-down.
